    "body": "hey @johanschaap if you do want to use the relative path you will need to remove `=` otherwise we are unable to properly parse it. So the command will be \r\n\r\n```\r\n./prysm..sh beacon-chain --http-web3provider ~/.ethereum/goerli/geth.ipc\r\n```\r\nusing `=` prevents the shell from correctly expanding the path. \r\n",
